response.overview: In the near future, Major is the first of her kind: a human saved from a terrible crash, then cyber-enhanced to be a perfect soldier devoted to stopping the world's most dangerous criminals.
response.tagline: There's nothing sadder than a puppet without a ghost.
response.title: Ghost in the Shell
